      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En d\\'eduire $ \\displaystyle{ S_n(x)=\\frac{1}{2\\pi}\\int \n_{-\\pi}^\\pi f(x+\\theta ) \\frac{\\sin (n+\\frac{1}{2})\\theta}\n{\\sin \\frac{\\theta }{2}}d\\theta } $.",
        "html": "<p>En déduire <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\displaystyle{ S_n(x)=\\frac{1}{2\\pi}\\int \n_{-\\pi}^\\pi f(x+\\theta ) \\frac{\\sin (n+\\frac{1}{2})\\theta}\n{\\sin \\frac{\\theta }{2}}d\\theta }\\)</span>.</p>\n"
